phrases: The Titan boy and his companions were summoned by the King.
They will be passing through the city today.
He is going to wind up getting dissected for sure this time.
Either way, I just hope things work out so they will seal the gates.
Did you just say seal the gates?
Do you want to further defile our gods with lowly human meddling?!
How dare you even suggest desecrating our three sacred goddesses?!
He is one of those crazies who worship the Walls as gods.
The Walls and nothing else are our protectors!
You looked so scary in your sleep nobody dared to wake you up.
You have been slacking off a lot recently.
How are we supposed to get along?
She is the only person in this branch with any actual combat experience.
Of course she cannot smile cheerfully when she is just returned from hell.
I wonder what you see in her.
There is only one way a dimwitted chick like you gets into the Military Police.
Today you will be doing something other than your usual chores.
That is why I ordered you to assemble here.
A unit from the Recon Corps has been summoned by the King.
They are passing through the city's main street today.
Escorting them to the capitol is Military Police HQ's responsibility,
so we only need to accompany them as they pass through town.
The use of 3D Maneuver Gear will be temporarily permitted within city limits.
You will guard the convoy in tandem with their own security.
You will travel by barge to the mission starting point.
What are we protecting the convoy from?
I am unaware of any people within this Wall who would oppose the King.
Even if we have overlooked some petty criminals,
truly organized opposition would be unimaginable, unless they had a stronghold outside the Wall.
Why would anyone even try such a thing in the first place?
Oh, well are not you clever?
I am putting you in charge.
Just do not screw it up.
The Military Police are even more rotten than I imagined.
That is why I picked being an MP, but still...
They force us rookies to handle everything.
They cannot think of anything but themselves.
What are you talking about, Marlo?
I am not scum like you guys.
I came here to correct the Military Police!
So that is how you roll?
And how will you fix things?
I will have to work my way to the top.
When I am in charge, I will enforce the rules and punish corruption.
I will make the Police a place for normal people again.
The way humans are meant to be!
Holy shit, you are the real deal!
Here I thought you were a total bore!
What a noble goal you have.
If a good person like you controlled the system,
that would be the end for us, I think.
You say all the correct things.
I know another person much like you.
You need a lot of courage to go against the greater flow.
But that does not mean you are not an idiot.
Maybe it is just that the other person you know is an idiot.
We have wasted too much time talking.
The convoy will pass through the outer gate in 45 minutes.
Once we are there, everyone confirm your designated positions.
They must be taking them to the Inner District.
Even so, having the merchants involved is unusual.
They are selling our emergency backups?!
Holy shit, he really is the real deal!
Guess we will see if that is for better or for worse...
For now let us just enjoy the show.
Let us grab a drink then.
E-Embezzling emergency backup supplies is a crime!
Emergency goods are paid for by the people's tax dollars and...
So you think you can lecture your superiors, rookie?
I look forward to your future.
For now, go buy yourself a hooker and chill the fuck out.
I will have you arrested for insubordination and treason.
I think that is probably enough.
Sorry if this retard was causing you trouble.
We will be sure he learns his lesson.
You would prefer to make a bigger scene?
We will let you off this once.
Let us go grab that drink now.
Were not you going to punish corruption?
If you want, I will help out.
What did you want to get?
We know you are working really hard!
Oh, I am not worthy of your praise.
Then I am just another piece of trash, caught up in that greater flow you mentioned earlier.
But is not that what normal human beings do?
I do not care if I am swept along by the flow, as long as I am still considered a human.
You are fitting in well with the Military Police.
I disguised myself as a porter.
The cloak can hide my 3D Maneuver Gear.
Annie, would you assist me in letting Eren escape?
Where could you go inside these Walls after disobeying the King?
We would just hide out for a while.
We do not intend to go against the King head-on.
It will be reported as a rebellion by a portion of the Recon Corps.
Time to collect proof that could change the outcome of the court martial.
Does anything so convenient even exist?
I am sorry too, but I cannot help you like this.
Good luck with whatever you are doing.
They are going to wind up executing Eren!
Clueless people will push mankind down the path of extinction
just for personal gain, without even realizing it!
I know my reasoning is not all that convincing.
Gambling big is our only chance at this point!
Of course, we will do our utmost to avoid causing trouble for you.
But to get through the security inside Wall Sina,
we need insider help from the Military Police.
Do I look like such a good person to you?
I do not like that term.
To me, it seems like the meaning of good person is really a person who is good for you.
In that sense, I do not think any individual can be good in everyone is eyes.
So if you do not help us...
Then, in my eyes, you would be a bad person.
We made it through more easily than I expected.
That is the Military Police for you.
You can tell how hard they work.
Let us just hope they do not discover Jean's taken my place.
I doubt that cover will last long.
You both share a villainous face and a sociopathic look in your eyes.
I do not have a horseface like him!
Hey, if I did not agree to help, how were you planning to get over the Wall?
I was going to use the 3D Maneuver Gear to break through.
Would not it have been less troublesome to escape before you reached Stohess?
I thought the dense layout of the urban area
would give us a better shot at swapping Jean for Eren.
Plus, pretending to follow obediently instead of opposing them outright will buy us more time to flee.
It is the abandoned remains of an underground city they planned long ago.
This leads as far as the outer gate.
Do not tell me you are scared of cramped, dark places?
I doubt a brave, borderline-suicidal guy like you could possibly understand the feelings of a weak maiden like me.
Someone who can fling a man head over heels in mid-air with ease cannot call herself a maiden.
Stop being silly and hurry up!
No, I am not going that way.
If we do not travel above ground, I will not help.
It should not be an issue, right, Mikasa?
For some reason, there have not been any people nearby for a while now.
When did you start looking at me with those eyes, Armin?
Why did you have Marco's 3D Maneuver Gear?
I recognized even its tiniest marks and dings
Well, I happened to pick it up.
Then you killed those two Titans we captured alive?
But if you thought so a month ago, why did not you act?
Because I could not believe it!
I still hope it is just some misunderstanding!
Since you... did not kill me back then...
That is why this is happening right now.
Yeah, I am pretty sure you are right.
I never expected you to corner me like this.
Why did not I kill you then?
There is still a chance that you have just got a sick sense of humor,
and you are just going along with whatever Armin says because you are an idiot.
If you come underground, that alone proves something!
I have failed to become a soldier.
I cannot listen to another word of this.
I will tear you apart once again,
I am glad I could be a good person for you.
But this is where my gamble begins!
The female-form Titan's true identity is revealed to be Annie Leonhardt.
However, Eren is unable to transform to confront her.
For him, she is still just Annie.
The Military Police (pt 1) While there are only about 2000 members of the Military Police, they also control the Garrison, making them roughly 5000 strong.
The Military Police (pt 2) Each walled city has about 200 MPs stationed there.
Their main duties are to oversee the training of cadets, monitor the Garrison, and direct fire-fighting operations in their area.
This is a victory for us!
Let us celebrate this victory for the next battle!
I died for naught I will not let it end like that for you
until I am the last one standing
In our hands we hold blades of glory
and sing in the name of victory
We bear the wings of freedom on our backs
Swearing iron determination upon our hearts,
we slash apart the circle of idiocy
Feiern wir diesen Sieg fr den nchsten Kampf
suna no utsuwa wo kowashite koboreta
fukai yami wo ore wa arukidashita
oretachi wa kabe no soto e
mata aouze chizu ni nai bashode
If we suppose that I am not me,
Can you say with certainty that you are you?
Will you be able to pick up after yourself
Once your sand-like she will breaks and your heart crumbles?
But now my ears are just ringing
It is as if time has frozen
I began to walk through a deep dark abyss
As swift as a gale, I escaped for my life
I felt like a living corpse
We break out of our walls
To reunite in worlds we have yet to map
